OL,6,FCatherine O'Connor was only 17 when
OL,7,Fshe bled out on an operating table at
OL,8,FSalford Royal Hospital in 2007.
OL,10,FThe teenager, born with spina bifida,
OL,11,Fhad hoped surgery to straighten her
OL,12,Fspine would change her life. It would
OL,13,Ftake years and three commissioned
OL,14,Freports for Catherine's family to find
OL,15,Fout what really happened.
