OL,6,FThe commissioned by the Northern Care
OL,7,FAlliance and published in March,
OL,8,Fconcluded the 'unacceptable' and
OL,9,F'unjustifiable' actions of her surgeon
OL,10,FJohn Bradley Williamson 'directly
OL,11,Fcontributed' to her death.
OL,13,FMr Williamson had pressed on with the
OL,14,Fhigh risk surgery despite never having
OL,15,Fdone it before and being explicitly
