OL,6,FEmily Bhogal was 12 when Mr Williamson
OL,7,Fcarried out surgery to treat her
OL,8,FScoliosis. She had two metal rods and
OL,9,F10 screws inserted into her back. Days
OL,10,Fafter surgery she collapsed with a
OL,11,Flife threatening medical condition
OL,12,Fwhich the surgeon denied was related
OL,13,Fto the operation.
OL,15,FShe has since found out at least five
OL,16,Fof the screws were put in the wrong
OL,17,Fplace.
