OL,6,FEmily said: "I just constantly feel as
OL,7,Fif my rods are being torn out of my
OL,8,Fback. It feels as if they are moving
OL,9,Fconstantly and it doesn't feel as if
OL,10,Fthey are in place. It doesn't feel as
OL,11,Fif they are where they are supposed to
OL,12,Fbe."
OL,14,FThe mother of one said: "When I
OL,15,Finitially had the surgery my posture
OL,16,Fwas very straight. Now I can't sit
OL,17,Fback in a chair I am constantly leant
OL,18,Fforward. I have no flexibility in my
OL,19,Fspine whatsoever so I struggle on a
OL,20,Fday to day basis getting up, getting
OL,21,Fdressed.
