OL,6,FIn March, Emily received a letter
OL,7,Fsaying her treatment had been reviewed
OL,8,Fas part of an investigation by the
OL,9,FRoyal Manchester Children's Hospital.
OL,10,FTheir findings concluded: "There was
OL,11,Fno harm resulting from your spinal
OL,12,Fsurgery... the spinal team noted a
OL,13,Fgood correction of the shape of your
OL,14,Fspine with appropriate position of
OL,15,Frods and screws."
OL,17,FBut her current spinal surgeon, who
OL,18,Fhas examined her in person, has
OL,19,Fconfirmed at least five of the ten
OL,20,Fscrews in her back are misplaced.
